  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> *</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 19 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 7 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 20</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H, M</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You create one or more kama or kusari-gama, made from solidified, golden spider silk (choose which type when performing this technique). The technique's cost is based on the weapon(s) created. The weapons are always made for your size, have a hardness of 5 and 7 HP. You are always proficient with the created weapons. When the technique ends, the weapons turn into ordinary spider silk threads.<br><br>Kama: The weapon acts like a normal kama, but deals one bonus piercing damage. A single kama costs 2 Chakra, and you can create up to 1 per 3 levels.<br><br>Kusari-gama: The weapon acts like a normal kusarigama, but you gain a +1 bonus to attack rolls made with it. A single kusari-gama costs 3 Chakra, and you can create up to 1 per 5 levels.</p>\n\n\n\n",
